## TiDB Compute Code Layout

Available at contrib/tidb/pkg/executor/ and contrib/tidb/pkg/expression/ — use read_file, search_code, and list_dir tools to explore.

The following shows code location of common executors:
- aggregation: pkg/executor/aggfuncs, pkg/executor/aggfunc
- join: pkg/executor/join
- sort or topn: pkg/executor/sortexec
- union: pkg/executor/unionexec
- cte: pkg/executor/cte.go
- window: pkg/executor/window.go
- apply: pkg/executor/parallel_apply.go

If not listed above, you can refer to the `executorBuilder.build` function in pkg/executor/builder.go to find the code location of one executor.

All functions used in tidb are located in pkg/expression/ directory.

Memory tracker is a very important tool in tidb executors as it tracks and control memory usage in tidb, you can find codes in pkg/util/memory/tracker.go. Similarily, disk tracker is in pkg/util/disk/tracker.go. Disk tracker is mainly used for spill in the tidb executor.

